Package svgger.stdlib

Standard library functions covering basic functionality of the language.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GoTo
    Standard function that moves the pen absolutely.
    Move
    Standard function that moves the pen relatively.
    PenDown
    Standard function that sets the pen down.
    PenUp
    Standard function that sets the pen up.
    ReturnIfZero
    Standard function that stops execution of the caller if an argument equals zero.
    SetColor
    Standard function that sets the color for the lines.
    SetRandomColor
    Standard function that sets the color for the lines.
    SetWidth
    Standard function that sets the width for the lines.
    StandardLibrary
    Class representing standard library.
    TurnLeft
    Standard function that turns the pen left.
    TurnRight
    Standard function that turns the pen right.
